v0.1 (201?-??-??):  initial version by Hui Zhou
                    applied to plot density of states (DOS)
                    <requirement: DOSCAR, CONTCAR>

v0.2 (2019-03-19):

v0.3 (2019-04-11):  add plot_plus_tot for LDOS

v0.4 (2019-04-14):  support for plotting `f-orbital`

v0.5 (2019-04-20):  simplify the plot API

v0.6 (2019-04-22):  optimization, read `DOSCAR, CONTCAR` files only once

v0.7 (2019-04-25):  support for reading multiple DOSCAR files

v0.8 (2019-04-26):  modify linewidth global

v1.0 (2019-05-25):  fit the DOSCAR data using `cubic`
                    add `color` parameters to control line color 

v1.1 (2019-06-23):  provide `fill` option to plot DOS
                    support band-center calculation

v1.2 (2019-07-27):  optimization, substitute `re` with line number to parse DOSCAR
                    rewrite doscar_parse with Cython
                    <requirement: Cython>

v1.3 (2019-10-17):  simplify line-type API, plot DOS use `fill`, `line` or `dash line` option

v1.4 (2021-05-24):  support output the DOSCAR data, only need set method=output 

v1.5 (2022-05-07):  add calculation of average DOS (divided by atoms number)
                    unify the parameters name (e.g., atom --> atoms)

v1.6 (2022-07-16):  simplify the PlotDOS API, remove the <class DOS>